 What people are saying about Cambium Learning:


                	As a school system with a long track record with Kurzweil 3000, we've seen students' reading skills increase by as much as 2 or 3 grade levels within a single semester. Tom Turner, School Administrator, Chouteau Public Schools, Chouteau, OK


                	One Gizmo in the hand of a math or science teacher can provide almost limitless opportunities for conceptual and extended learning. Leslie Accardo, Model Schools Coordinator, Lower Hudson Regional Information Center, NY


                	The support we receive from our Voyager Sopris partners has consistently been reliable, professional, and personal.  I appreciate their eagerness�to assist our district with problem solving and building internal capacity. Deanna Parish, Coordinator of Curriculum & Instruction, Department of Exceptional Children Services,Charleston County School District, SC




                	My class of kindergarten students LOVE going on Raz-Kids. Often, they go there for their free time play. They are highly motivated to read and I find it a wonderful way to get leveled books into the hands of my early readers. Bless you all, for what you are providing for education! Birdy Hartman, Teacher, San Diego, CA


                	Our teachers are completely behind Reflex because they are seeing an amazing change in our students' math skills. Mary Armstrong, Math Instructional Facilitator, Bryant School District 25, AR


















